description: Activiti is a light-weight workflow and Business Process Management (BPM) Platform targeted at business people, developers and system admins. Activiti runs in any Java application, on a server, on a cluster or in the cloud. It integrates perfectly with Spring, it is extremely lightweight and based on simple concepts.
